WEBVTT

00:01:29.220 --> 00:01:33.300
to prison inmates who carry
a hell of pain inside their hearts,

00:01:33.820 --> 00:01:38.060
and to those, many of them young,
who cannot find a job,

00:01:38.940 --> 00:01:41.740
I often find myself wondering:

00:01:43.460 --> 00:01:46.555
"Why them and not me?"

00:01:49.055 --> 00:01:52.928
I, myself, was born
in a family of migrants;

00:01:54.540 --> 00:01:59.956
my father, my grandparents,
like many other Italians,

00:01:59.980 --> 00:02:02.036
left for Argentina